<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#A0A1A7;--shiki-light-font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#7F848E;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic;">// 要么 a的M位为1, b的M位为0; 要么 b的M位为1, a的M位为0;</span></span>
